- landing_page_target = "law_enforcement"

.signup-landing-page.landing-page{ class: "signup-landing-page-#{landing_page_target}" }
  %header.banner-header
    .container
      .row
        .icon-wrapper
          = render "/landing_pages/icons/header_#{landing_page_target}_svg"
        .banner-text
          %h1
            Bike Index for Law Enforcement
          %h3
            Is your department equipped to fight bike theft? Bike Index can help
            you get bikes back into the right hands.

    .ribbon.mobile-contact-link
      .container
        %h2
          = link_to "Sign up for free", new_organization_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg"

  .container
    .row.main-body-row
      .landing-why-col
        %h3
          Recover your citizen's bikes

        %p
          You're the first one your citizens look to when their bikes are
          stolen. Access and search our international database to return your
          community's bikes to their rightful owners.

        %p
          You have the authority to bring bikes back - that’s no small
          responsibility. That’s why we have tools - such as our integration
          with LeadsOnline and #{link_to "automated tweets", "https://twitter.com/stolenbikessfo"}
          of stolen bikes - to keep your community safe. Connect with
          #{link_to "local ambassadors", "http://bikeindex.org/ambassadors_how_to"}
          and spotters to quickly confiscate and block sales of stolen bikes.

        %p
          With over 215,000 registries and almost 5,500 stolen bicycle
          recoveries, we know how to help.


        %p
          = render partial: "/landing_pages/tweet", locals: { tweet_id: 839247587521679360 }

        %h3 Put a lock on bike theft

        %p
          Our extensive archive has helped officers recover bikes involved in
          criminal situations, from simple theft to chop shops, drug houses -
          even fencing rings and online black markets.

        %p
          With over 600 partnerships, Bike Index is the industry leader in
          bicycle registration. Join our network for free
          #{link_to "here", "https://bikeindex.org/organizations/new"},
          or ask us to put you in touch with an existing partner in law
          enforcement.

        %p
          If you want to collaborate with other departments in your city to
          manage a registry, learn more about Bike Index for municipalities
          #{link_to "here", for_cities_path}.

        %p
          = render partial: "/landing_pages/tweet", locals: { tweet_id: 890211853942407168 }

        %h4 Related articles:
        %ul
          %li
            = link_to "Bend reduces bike theft by 60 percent",
            "https://bikeindex.org/news/bend-reduces-bike-theft-by-60-percent-with-help-from-pine-mountain-spo"
          %li
            = link_to "Bike Index's newest municipal partner: New Orleans",
            "https://bikeindex.org/news/bike-indexs-newest-municipal-partner-new-orleans"

        .trusted-by.hidden-lg-up
          %h3
            Trusted by Law Enforcement everywhere
          = image_tag "landing_pages/logos/law-enforcement.png", alt: "law enforcement partners"

      .next-steps-col
        .next-steps-wrap
          %header
            Trusted by law enforcement everywhere
            = link_to "Sign up for free", new_organization_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg"
          .trusted-by
            .header
              Trusted by law enforcement everywhere
            = image_tag "landing_pages/logos/law-enforcement.png", alt: "law enforcement partners"
